1. open a terminal 
2. enter subl ~/.bashrc or vim ~/.bashrc
3. take pycharm as an example:
   add below lines:
   1) export PATH=/media/dongmeng/Software/pycharm_ubuntu/pycharm-community-2018.1.4/bin:${PATH}
   2) alias pycharm='(pycharm.sh > /tmp/pycharm.log &)'  # (...&) keeps the program valid even if closing the terminal
   save and close
4. source ~/.bashrc  #make it valid
